---
title: GitHub CI Workflows
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant FB as Feature Branch
    participant D as development
    participant M as master
    participant NPM as npm registry

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over FB,D: PR → development
        Dev->>FB: push changes
        FB->>D: open PR
        activate D
        D->>D: lint
        D->>D: test
        D->>D: typecheck
        D->>D: build
        deactivate D
        D-->>FB: checks pass
        Dev->>D: merge PR
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over D,M: PR → master
        Dev->>D: open PR to master
        activate M
        M->>M: build
        deactivate M
        M-->>D: checks pass
        Dev->>M: merge PR
    end

    rect rgb(224, 255, 230)
        Note over M,NPM: Push → master (post-merge)
        activate M
        M->>M: lint
        M->>M: test
        M->>M: typecheck
        M->>M: build
        M->>M: commit build/<br/>[BUILD]: update build output
        deactivate M
        Dev->>NPM: npm publish (manual)
    end
